OL,3,CPolice chief suspended over 'conduct
OL,4,Callegations'
OL,6,FThe chief constable of Staffordshire
OL,7,Fhas been suspended following
OL,8,Fallegations about his conduct.
OL,10,FThe Staffordshire Commissioner for
OL,11,FPolice, Fire and Rescue, Ben Adams
OL,12,Fconfirmed the news and said he is now
OL,13,Flooking to name a temporary chief
OL,14,Fconstable.
OL,16,FChris Noble was reported to the
OL,17,FIndependent Office of Police Conduct
OL,18,Flast year.
