OL,3,CPolice chief suspended over 'conduct
OL,4,Callegations'
OL,6,FThe investigation over his referral is
OL,7,Fsaid to be 'ongoing' while additional
OL,8,Fallegations have now been made against
OL,9,Fthe former Chief Constable.
OL,11,FThe watchdog said it is also looking
OL,12,Fat allegations that Mr Noble shared
OL,13,Fconfidential information without a
OL,14,Fpolicing purpose.
OL,16,FAdditional allegations have since been
OL,17,Fmade that "meet the threshold for
OL,18,Fsuspension" ` but the force says they
OL,19,Fare "not work related" and pre-date
OL,20,Fhis time at Staffordshire Police.
