OL,3,CPolice chief suspended over 'conduct
OL,4,Callegations'
OL,6,FMr Noble was promoted into the role in
OL,7,F2021 and had been a police officer for
OL,8,Fmore than 20 years.
OL,10,FHe was also Commander for Belfast City
OL,11,FPolicing District, with responsibility
OL,12,Ffor overt counter-terrorism policing,
OL,13,Flocal response and neighbourhood
OL,14,Fpolicing, along with public order and
OL,15,Fcivil contingencies.
OL,17,FHe swapped his role as Humberside
OL,18,FPolice's assistant chief constable to
OL,19,Ftake the senior role in Staffordshire.
