OL,3,CPolice chief suspended over 'conduct
OL,4,Callegations'
OL,6,FMr Noble will be suspended pending the
OL,7,Foutcome of the IOPC's ongoing
OL,8,Finvestigation.
OL,10,FMr Adams said: "Public confidence in
OL,11,Fthe police service is vital so all
OL,12,Fallegations of misconduct must be
OL,13,Ffully and independently investigated.
OL,15,F"In the interests of the public,
OL,16,FStaffordshire Police and the chief
OL,17,Fconstable himself, I have decided to
OL,18,Fsuspend Mr Noble from his role pending
OL,19,Fthe outcome of the IOPC's
OL,20,Finvestigation.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
