OL,3,CPolice chief suspended over 'conduct
OL,4,Callegations'
OL,6,F"Suspension is a neutral act, to
OL,7,Fenable an independent and thorough
OL,8,Finvestigation to take place. It has no
OL,9,Fbearing on any indication of guilt and
OL,10,Fshould not be seen as such.
OL,12,F"I know that this announcement will
OL,13,Fcome as a shock to many across
OL,14,FStaffordshire, especially our hard-
OL,15,Fworking officers and staff, but it is
OL,16,Fright that allegations of this serious
OL,17,Fnature are dealt with consistently and
OL,18,Finvestigated properly and thoroughly.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
