OL,6,F"I continue to be focused on the
OL,7,Fcommunities of Staffordshire and Stoke-
OL,8,Fon-Trent, and ensuring that
OL,9,FStaffordshire Police continues to keep
OL,10,Four residents safe, protect the
OL,11,Fvulnerable, and prevent and detect
OL,12,Fcrime and anti-social behaviour.
