OL,3,CPolice chief suspended over 'conduct
OL,4,Callegations'
OL,6,F"My team is now working to identify a
OL,7,Ftemporary Chief Constable. As this is
OL,8,Fan ongoing investigation by the IOPC,
OL,9,FI will not be commenting further."
OL,11,FIn a statement, an IOPC spokesman
OL,12,Fsaid: "We received mandatory referrals
OL,13,Ffrom Staffordshire's Office of the
OL,14,FPolice, Fire & Crime Commissioner on
OL,15,FApril 30, June 27 and July 29 this
OL,16,Fyear in relation to Staffordshire
OL,17,FPolice Chief Constable Chris Noble.
