OL,3,CPolice chief suspended over 'conduct
OL,4,Callegations'
OL,6,F"The referrals relate to reports we've
OL,7,Freceived raising serious concerns over
OL,8,FMr Noble's behaviour outside of his
OL,9,Fwork duties.
OL,11,F"The matters pre-date Mr Noble's
OL,12,Fappointment as Chief Constable for
OL,13,FStaffordshire Police.
OL,15,F"The IOPC is also separately
OL,16,Finvestigating Mr Noble over
OL,17,Fallegations he shared confidential
OL,18,Finformation without proper policing
OL,19,Fpurpose.
